  <p class="mb-5 leading-relaxed">Welcome to the Wavey Dynamics Podcast.</p>
  <p class="mb-5 leading-relaxed">This is a place for engineering professionals, enthusiasts and fans to tune in to conversations with motorsport's finest engineers.</p>
  <p class="mb-5 leading-relaxed">Through our work in motorsport engineering we often find ourselves having great, highly technical conversations with engineers working at the forefront of their field in F1, GT, WEC and more. It occurred to us that you might love for these conversations as much as we do.</p>
